Package pokemon.model

Class Summary
Cart Class for handling the pokemons in the cart
CartManager Class for managing the carts of different users
CartPokemon Class which is derived from the pokemon-class and extends it by further features for handling pokemons in an onlineshop-cart
Pokemon Class containing basic information on a pokemon
SessionConstants Class containing constans for handling session-attributes
User Class for storing basic information about a user
UserManager Class for managing the users stores the users in a list and can verify the login of each user
